posting_body: ['Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'x 20', 'OR Text', '20', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text with us.', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath, approximately 1125-1150 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'We are centrally located in Renton, just one minute from Highway 167, three minutes from I-405, and five minutes from I-5.', "Borgata's location is on a quiet street combines the safety and security of a neighborhood with the ease of apartment living.", "Our comfortable townhomes and flats are clustered along a leafy cul-de-sac on a hillside above Renton, with views of the city's twinkling lights below.", 'Our spacious 1, 2 and 3-bedroom apartments and townhomes feature nine-foot ceilings and oversized windows, patios, decks and gas fireplaces.', 'Make an appointment to visit Borgata Apartments and Townhomes in Renton today - our staff will welcome you, and our community will charm you!', 'Features:', 'Individual Climate Control, Gas Fireplace, Cable Ready, Additional Storage Units, Wheel Chair Access, Microwave, Full-Size Refrigerator, Garbage Disposal, Window Coverings, Large Closets, In Unit Washer & Dryer, Private Balcony or Patio, Dishwasher', 'Community Amenities:', 'Fitness Center, Attached Garage*, Storage Space, On-Site Maintenance Available, Reserved Covered Parking and Attached Garages*, Outdoor Swimming Pool and Spa, Community Events, Business Center, Friendly, Responsive On-Site Management Staff, Package Receiving, Security Patrol, Clubhouse, Close to Public Transportation', 'Pet Policy', 'Pets - Max 2 allowed, One time Fee $300, Deposit $200', 'Cat Rent $35/mnth', 'Dog Rent $50/mnth', 'Follow This Link for More Information:', '<URL>', 'Photos and/or floor plans shown are representational and may not depict the exact layout or features of the available unit.', "If currently occupied, the individual unit you've selected may not be available to tour.", 'Please contact our leasing team with any questions.', '226TzbsAEeSM']
